{"tid":277552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工黨黨魁郝爾彬慶祝欲擊掌　一手錯拍女幕僚胸部","createTime":"2017-06-09T16:29:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T04:16:37.000Z","uid":5195,"like":85,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d8a16c46f38b3502a3e43497d67d36296323f605","tid":277552,"uid":5195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T16:29:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/midas/ddb9de665fe0cce7f453f03a10232a2b/205357954/giphy+%282%29.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fo.aolcdn.com%2Fhss%2Fstorage%2Fmidas%2Fddb9de665fe0cce7f453f03a10232a2b%2F205357954%2Fgiphy%2B%25282%2529.gif&h=5edc000f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國工黨黨魁郝爾彬較早時前往北伊斯靈頓選區點票場地，視察點票結果。當他獲悉勝出後，興奮得與其女幕僚振臂歡呼。期間郝爾彬欲與她擊掌之際，卻錯手拍中她的胸部，此尷尬一幕被上載至互聯網，惹來網民熱議。<br />\n<br />\n事發於北伊斯靈頓的點票場地，郝爾彬獲悉勝出後，向支持者表示：「感覺好極了」。他之後與其影子內閣外交大臣方璧琳振臂慶祝，大家笑逐顏開之時，卻上演有趣一幕。事源郝爾彬欲與她擊掌慶祝，但對方沒有留意到而舉手回應，令郝爾彬不慎一手拍在她的胸部。幸而方璧琳表現得對此完全沒有反應，就像一切不曾發生一樣，化解本來會尷尬萬分的情境。"},{"pid":"943dcb9d4d5e08b9ddb8565261636ac58ed45ace","tid":277552,"uid":5195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T16:29:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.huffingtonpost.com/asset/scalefit_630_noupscale/593a47bb1d00002900cc2065.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.huffingtonpost.com%2Fasset%2Fscalefit_630_noupscale%2F593a47bb1d00002900cc2065.gif&h=ab7b604c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8d5427bf0daf1a223f91565e4f442aa326fbcb6","tid":277552,"uid":73849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T16:31:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.huffingtonpost.com/asset/scalefit_630_noupscale/593a47bb1d00002900cc2065.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.huffingtonpost.com%2Fasset%2Fscalefit_630_noupscale%2F593a47bb1d00002900cc2065.gif&h=ab7b604c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"